      <h2>Request a Free Removal Quote</h2>
      <p>Tell us your zip code and we'll connect you with a vetted provider in your area — usually within the hour.</p>
      <iframe data-tally-src="https://tally.so/embed/0QL69P?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1&dynamicHeight=1" width="100%" height="320" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" title="Homeowner Request Form"></iframe>
    </div>

    <h2 id="service-areas">Service Areas Across South Florida</h2>
    <p>We connect homeowners with licensed providers across all major South Florida counties. Select your area for local removal specialists:</p>

